longBusinessSummary: Aptus Value Housing Finance India Limited, together with its subsidiary, Aptus Finance India Private Limited, operates as a housing finance company in India. The company offers home construction, purchase, renovation, and extension loans; and loans against property for construction and purchase of houses; and credit shield and property insurance, as well as small business and top-up loans. It serves the self-employed, and low-and middle-income families from rural and semi urban areas. Aptus Value Housing Finance India Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Chennai, India.
